<div class="jumbotron">

  <h1>Welcome to Metro Post</h1>
  <p>Metro Post is a place to share information about the LA metro rail service.</p>
  <div class='circles-jumbo'>
    <%=	image_tag 'gold-circle.png', 'class' => 'circle-img-jumbo'%>
    <%=	image_tag 'red-circle.png', 'class' => 'circle-img-jumbo'%>
    <%=	image_tag 'purple-circle.png', 'class' => 'circle-img-jumbo'%>
    <%=	image_tag 'blue-circle.png', 'class' => 'circle-img-jumbo'%>
    <%=	image_tag 'expo-circle.png', 'class' => 'circle-img-jumbo'%>
    <%=	image_tag 'green-circle.png', 'class' => 'circle-img-jumbo'%>
  </div>

  <!-- hide sign up button upon login -->
  <% unless current_user %>
    <p> <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_path, 'class' => 'btn btn-primary btn-lg' %> </p>
  <% end %>

</div>

<div class="container">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="marketing">
        <% if current_user %>
          <%=	link_to image_tag('post-icon.png'), new_comment_path %>
        <% else	%>
          <%=	link_to image_tag('post-icon.png'), new_session_path %>
        <% end %>
        <h2>Make A Post</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        If you haven't created an account yet, go ahead and
        <%= link_to 'sign up now', new_user_path, 'class' => 'btn btn-primary btn-xs' %>.
        Then, make a post about the LA metro.
        First, pick the line (or lines) you would like to comment on.
        Create a title and body for your post.
        Then, click submit.  It's that easy.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="marketing">
        <% if current_user %>
          <%=	link_to image_tag('fav-icon.png'), favorites_path %>
        <% else	%>
          <%=	link_to image_tag('fav-icon.png'), new_session_path %>
        <% end	%>
        <h2>Star A Line</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        Now that you've signed up, you can create some favorite lines.
        This will help to tailor your feed with only the most relevant information.
        If you don't want any favorites, no problem, you can check out information
        for every Metro line.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="marketing">
        <% if current_user %>
          <%=	link_to image_tag('info-icon.png'), comments_path %>
        <% else	%>
          <%=	link_to image_tag('info-icon.png'), new_session_path %>
        <% end	%>
        <h2>Stay Informed</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        Once you've got some favorite lines, we'll tailor your feed so you
        only see information about the lines you use and care about.
        When you make posts about a specific line,
        you'll be helping to keep the community informed about what's
        happening on the LA Metro.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>







